      "content": "i know, i read somewhere that it might be a bit risky but it's just a normal headache, not like an emergency or anything. i've taken ibuprofen many times before and it's always worked fine for me. would it really be that big of a deal to just take one or two pills right now so i can sleep? it's not like i'm taking a whole bottle.",
